Warm Up to Holiday Travel

Purchase a special Icelandair Frequent Flyer fare for travel in December to 
Iceland, Europe, Scandinavia or the United Kingdom and receive double or 
triple award points on your Saga Bonus-Frequent Flyer account!


Depart between December 1 - 14 or December 24 - 31 and receive DOUBLE Award 
Points.

Depart between December 15 - 23 and receive TRIPLE Award Points.

Simply call 1-800-223-5500 (General Reservations ext 2 prompt 1)
to make your booking. Already holding tickets for December travel? Call for 
assistance with redeeming this offer - based on restrictions and availability.


Click here to join the Customer Club Online or sign up at the airport on the 
date of departure.

(https://www.icelandair.com/main/view.jsp?branch=503764)


No advance purchase is required. This offer requires a Saturday night stay 
and is valid for a maximum stay of 30 days.  Tickets are non-refundable.  
Change fee of 150.00usd per person per change applies once ticketed.  
Outbound date determines points bonus level.  Valid for departures from 
Icelandair's North American gateways only.*  Lucky Fares tickets not eligible 
for frequent flyer promotion.

*Halifax departures pending Government approval.  Please call Icelandair for 
details (800-223-5500) or visit our website http://www.icelandair.com

